{"tid":1324830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[逃犯邊條例?] 軍刀攞命：27歲「洗頭仔」大陸落網移交香港警方","createTime":"2019-07-16T16:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T23:53:36.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"72a15feaf0ce07a2c966ab91277e9b8984b5c51d","tid":1324830,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:22:19.000Z","msg":"元朗本月6日發生謀殺案，27歲姓張髮型屋「洗頭仔」，涉嫌擸刀桶死女同事的17歲男友人後潛逃內地。香港警方掌握其資料後，向公安部、廣東省公安廳及深圳市公安局要求協助，該名潛逃的疑兇最後在內地落網。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Uz4KBkNbyN.IYQ3WzAVw2g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-07/46257af0-a7c8-11e9-bff2-acba60ee57fc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUz4KBkNbyN.IYQ3WzAVw2g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-07%2F46257af0-a7c8-11e9-bff2-acba60ee57fc&h=5f25b227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日(16日)，<span style=\"color: red;\">警方在落馬洲口岸接收由內地執法機關送回的該名涉案疑犯</span>。香港警方感謝公安部、廣東省公安廳及深圳市公安局的全力協助，該名疑犯最終在內地落網，不但標誌着兩地警方對聯合打擊罪行的決心，更清晰地表達兩地警方對維護社會法治的信念。<br />\n<br />\n案發當日晚8時許，張在髮型屋內，不慎踩到素有積怨的女同事腳部，對方心感不忿向張理論，雙方爆發激烈口角，未幾女方「吹雞」召來姓黃事主，以及兩名分別姓袁及姓鄭（俱19歲）男友人到場「幫拖」。現場消息指，3名男子抵達紅棉圍後，在髮型屋附近街頭「恭候」。期間，張放工在店外被3人截停盤問，雙方發生爭執，突然有人情緒失控，從懷中取出一把6吋長的鋒利軍刀施襲，其中黃閃避不及，頭及身體多處被狂捅多刀，血如泉湧，他負傷突圍跑至合財街一個菜檔，終不支倒地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fMfom6vMe7Dnb4cIjmzjMw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-07/64699690-a7c8-11e9-bf77-61e6547896db\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FfMfom6vMe7Dnb4cIjmzjMw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-07%2F64699690-a7c8-11e9-bf77-61e6547896db&h=db525170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，涉案姓張疑兇則跑回髮型屋，更換染血恤衫及牛仔褲，並放下兇刀後逃去。黃如血人昏迷在街頭，經送院搶救後，延至當晚9時59分不治，死因需剖屍確定。其後，警方翻查出入境記錄，獲悉疑兇已於當晚9時17分，經羅湖口岸潛逃往內地，案件列作謀殺由元朗警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/25Jh0vOZjwKC9GNQJOCV5Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-07/175477b0-a045-11e9-b9ff-f3b3ad53ac07\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F25Jh0vOZjwKC9GNQJOCV5Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-07%2F175477b0-a045-11e9-b9ff-f3b3ad53ac07&h=a195bbeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38a415351229457fde1b98ee7d06b949cb7065c3","tid":1324830,"uid":197540,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"都有交接點解仲要逃犯條例？"},{"pid":"f05d48328fb60a92e0a6298ea5ccf6d30b93d007","tid":1324830,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38a415351229457fde1b98ee7d06b949cb7065c3","tid":1324830,"uid":197540,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"都有交接點解仲要逃犯條例？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adae06856fec188845b949adfcc8bd0c9590d8d1","tid":1324830,"uid":40716,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"38a415351229457fde1b98ee7d06b949cb7065c3","tid":1324830,"uid":197540,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"都有交接點解仲要逃犯條例？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:14:27.000Z","msg":"一直都係中國移犯畀香港 香港從來未移犯過去中國<br />\n而家就係要條例嚟送你中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8473f16d41061fae7745a1e554a2603650812e31","tid":1324830,"uid":56833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"adae06856fec188845b949adfcc8bd0c9590d8d1","tid":1324830,"uid":40716,"like":13,"dis